high_descs: In living room head towards the coffeetable
Take a peach from the wooden table.
Turn right to the sink side and turn right to the kitchen.
Turn right to the sink, place the peach in the sink and pour the water.
Take a fruit from the sink and turn right head towards and turn left to the door. Turn left to reach the coffeetable.
Place the peach on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Take the peach, clean it and keep it on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Walk straight across the room to reach the coffeetable.
Pick up the peach from the table.
Turn right to the middle of the room and walk to the right to head down the passage and turn right to reach the sink.
Wash the peach in the sink and take it out.
Turn right to access the passage and turn left to walk down the passage and turn left to reach the coffeetable.
Put the peach on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed peach on the coffeetable.

high_descs: Go straight to the coffee table
Pick the peach from the coffee table
Turn right go straight again turn right to the sink
Put the peach into the sink rinse it off and take it back
Turn right go straight turn left to the coffee table
Place the peach on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Pick the peach from the coffee table,clean it and place it on the coffee table
